# Hardware Connections

## Ultrasonic Sensor

VCC → 5V

GND → GND

TRIG → D9

ECHO → D10

---

## Servo Motor

Signal → D11

VCC → 5V

GND → GND

---

## L298N Motor Driver

IN1 → D2

IN2 → D3

IN3 → D4

IN4 → D5

---

## Power Supply

3 × 18650 Batteries

Connected to L298N Power Input

Arduino powered through 5V output of L298N
